title: Example sounds download of LDOCE5 (Plus), English Channel Inc.
description:
Example sounds file for LDOCE 5 (PLUS). For iOS users, unzip this zip file, and you get an LDOCE.dbpkg folder, move this LDOCE.dbpkg folder to Library/Contents. 

10 audio database files are included in this LDOCE.dbpkg folder:

ldoce_aifj.db
